    </div>

    <div class="main-page-wrapper variable-size">
        <h1 class="question">How can I join the team?</h1>
        <div>
            <p class="answer">
                If you have, or are working on getting your <a href="https://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/en/firearms/licensing">PAL</a> (Possession and Acquisition Licence)
                the team would love to take you out to the range.
                You'll get the chance to try a game of skeet, even if you don't have the equipment necessary!
                The best way to get in contact with the team is through any of the socials below or
                by using the <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
                We are an inclusive club, <b>no matter the skill level</b>, we want you!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-page-wrapper variable-size">
        <h1 class="question">What are events like?</h1>
        <div>
            <p class="answer">
                We normally hold events at <a href="https://www.sffgc.ca/">Smiths Falls Fish and Game Club</a>.
                This allows for us to have fun breaking clays and trying out Trap and 5-Stand.
                This is the perfect time for people who have never shot before, and those who've shot their whole life.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-page-wrapper variable-size">
        <h1 class="question">When is your next event?</h1>
        <div>
            <p class="answer">
                See our <a href="/events">events page</a>.
                <br>
                <br>
                <b>Note:</b> Due to the pandemic, we have suspended all practices and events until further notice.
            </p>
